training_data, scoring_data = make_test_data()
model = MLPClassifier(solver='lbfgs')
result = sklearn_sequential_forward_selection(model, training_data,
    scoring_data, peirce_skill_score, 'argmin')
validate_result(result)
result = sklearn_sequential_backward_selection(model, training_data,
    scoring_data, gerrity_score, 'argmin')
validate_result(result)
trained_model = model.fit(*training_data)
result = sklearn_permutation_importance(trained_model, scoring_data,
    heidke_skill_score, 'argmin')
validate_result(result)
